The Big Idea

Global Trade AI Brain

Instead of every company optimizing only its own supply chain, the system optimizes the entire network simultaneously.

Right now supply chains are locally optimized but globally inefficient.

Example today:

Company A ships product from China to Texas
Company B ships same product from Mexico to California

But maybe:

Company A should source from Mexico
Company B should source from China

Nobody sees the whole picture.

An AI network could.

