Layer 1 — The Global Supply Graph

The platform builds a giant graph of trade relationships.

Nodes:
	•	factories
	•	distributors
	•	warehouses
	•	carriers
	•	retailers
	•	ports

Edges:
	•	shipments
	•	contracts
	•	purchase orders
	•	logistics routes

Think of it like a map of global commerce.

